## Dataset Derivation

The Mars crater images used in this project are derived from the USGS Astrogeology Science Center's Thermal Emission Imaging System (THEMIS) Day IR Controlled Mosaic images. These can be accessed at the following link:

- [THEMIS Day IR Controlled Mosaic Images](https://pds-imaging.jpl.nasa.gov/volumes/ody.html)

The crater information, including latitude, longitude, and diameter, is sourced from the dataset compiled by Robbins and Hynek. This dataset can be accessed here:

- [Robbins and Hynek Mars Crater Database](https://craters.sjrdesign.net/)
